            <title>[SOLR-7778] Angular behaviour with no cores is incorrect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7778</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Angular UI should, when no cores are present, hide the main display and auto-pop-up the add core dialog.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, the core selector should be hidden when no cores exist.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
